{"tid":761742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大研究指港鐵列車開門時門邊空氣懸浮粒子會飆升","createTime":"2018-07-30T15:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T03:39:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"882ba72b2e0f136c7e93e7bd070c740731933fc2","tid":761742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/73/2018/07/30/6/6d7a3a48b7afc017aa093985fb4dca58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F73%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F6%2F6d7a3a48b7afc017aa093985fb4dca58.jpg&h=494434d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科大研究指出，港鐵列車開門的一剎那，車門門邊空氣的微細懸浮粒子PM2.5濃度會突然飆升，對健康有影響。<br />\n<br />\n負責研究的學者指，原因是車輪與路軌摩擦產生。港鐵回覆指，已參考環保署發出的守則，作出定期監察，確保車站和車廂空氣維持在良好水平。"},{"pid":"69479ab8760dab06ef3b239efc3ad8f999359d43","tid":761742,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"050b84d319be69dbeb50f871c71b73251d4aad58","tid":761742,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"香港人返工日日吸，宜家先講，個肺應該要換"},{"pid":"6841bbc4c4f43394dce579f7e0630efbbee6e6a1","tid":761742,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"衝閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df9bbe0dd803d937d37c26712fdf6302f837631","tid":761742,"uid":195944,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"話俾啲死都要企係門口嘅人聽就啱<br />\n話俾佢地聽企係門口會有肺癌 肺氣腫 哮喘<br />\n睇下佢地仲企唔企係門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560ad77d64be66ab036c303b201bb6923e6e051e","tid":761742,"uid":99700,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"原來D波板糖人既工作就係幫乘客吸懸浮粒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b391a3f61ecc921176eca7c2f4ef018decc11b","tid":761742,"uid":41317,"l